                "BodyEnglish": "The elevator connecting the parking deck to platform 1 is out of service. Platform 1 remains accessible via the station elevator. Visit the West Harbour GO Station page to find helpful information on departures, a station map and a listing of all the services we have available. Visit our Accessibility page to see how we are committed to making our services easy for everyone to use.",
