            {
                "Code": "M0000422312",
                "ParentCode": "M0000421388",
                "Status": "UPD",
                "PostedDateTime": "2024-04-02 22:02:40",
                "SubjectEnglish": "Stouffville Line Service Adjustment April 13 – 14",
                "SubjectFrench": "",
                "BodyEnglish": "Throughout the April 13 - 14 weekend, Stouffville GO train service will be adjusted for construction. GO buses will replace trains between Old Elm GO and Union Station as we work to improve your service. Note: Milliken, Agincourt, and Kennedy GO will not be served by any bus replacements. Customers will be directed to TTC. Transfer for free with one fare between GO Transit and the TTC.Click here to learn more.",
                "BodyFrench": "Tout au long de la fin de semaine du 13 au 14 avril, le service de Train GO de Stouffville sera rajusté en fonction de la construction. GO bus remplaceront les trains entre le vieux GO et la Gare Union alors que nous travaillons à améliorer votre service. Remarque : Milliken, Agincourt et Kennedy GO ne seront pas desservis par des remplaçants d’autobus. Les clients seront dirigés vers TTC. Transfert gratuit avec un tarif entre GO Transit et le TTC.Cliquez ici pour en savoir plus.",
                "Category": "General Information",
                "SubCategory": "GO Train General Service Alert",
                "Lines": [
