            {
                "Code": "M0000422725",
                "ParentCode": "M0000422724",
                "Status": "UPD",
                "PostedDateTime": "2024-04-06 17:03:37",
                "SubjectEnglish": "Construction at your station",
                "SubjectFrench": "Construction à votre station \r\n",
                "BodyEnglish": "The bus loop at your station has been closed for construction and the stop for GO Bus Route 68 has been relocated to Essa Road near Gowan Street. Please use the pedestrian tunnel to access Gowan Street and the temporary bus stops and do not walk on the tracks. Crossing tracks is dangerous and illegal.Train customers: this construction work will change how you get around your station. Please allow extra time to navigate around the construction areas.Here’s what you need to know: • The Lakeshore Dr. and Tiffin St. access to the pickup and drop-off area is closed (see map). You can still access the pickup and drop-off area from the eastern entrance.• Please be cautious around the construction area and follow directional signage. We will keep you updated as the project progresses.For more information on this project, please visit the city of Barrie website.",
                "BodyFrench": "La boucle de bus de votre gare a été fermée pour construction et l'arrêt pour GO Trajet d'autobus 68 a été déplacé sur Essa Road près de Gowan Street. Veuillez utiliser le tunnel piétonnier pour accéder à la rue Gowan et aux arrêts de bus temporaires et ne pas marcher sur les pistes. Traverser les voies est dangereux et illégal.Train clients : ce travail de construction va changer la façon dont vous vous déplacez autour de votre gare. Veuillez accorder plus de temps pour naviguer dans les zones de construction.Voici ce que vous devez savoir : · L’accès à la zone de collecte et de dépose-retour de Lakeshore Dr. et de la rue Tiffin est fermé (voir la carte). Vous pouvez toujours accéder à la zone de collecte et de dépose à partir de l'entrée est. · Soyez prudent autour de la zone de construction et suivez la signalisation directionnelle. Nous vous tiendrons informés au fur et à mesure du projet.Pour plus d'informations sur ce projet, veuillez visiter le site Web de la ville de Barrie.",
                "Category": "General Information",
                "SubCategory": "Station General Information",
                "Lines": [
                    {
                        "Code": "BR"
                    }
                ],
                "Stops": [
                    {
                        "Name": null,
                        "Code": "AD"
                    }
                ],
                "Trips": []
            },
            {
                "Code": "M0000422726",
                "ParentCode": "M0000422723",
                "Status": "UPD",
                "PostedDateTime": "2024-04-06 17:03:53",
                "SubjectEnglish": "Temporary bus stop relocation",
                "SubjectFrench": "",
                "BodyEnglish": "The area west of the station building is closed as part of the ongoing parking lot and bus loop rehabilitation project.Here’s what you need to know: · The sidewalk and doors on the west side of the station building will be fenced off for work.· North Pick up and Drop off and bus loop are fenced off.· Customers using the train platform can pass along the east side of the station building.· Customers can use the protected temporary pedestrian walkway installed to travel between the station and the relocated bus stops. o Northbound Buses: please board at street stop on Bridge St, east of Dissette St.o Southbound Buses: please board at street stop on Holland St East, west of Marshview Blvd. Please be cautious near and around construction areas.",
